outfit_data.top: A chunky knit cream-colored turtleneck sweater crafted from wool and cashmere blend. The neckline is high and slightly oversized, offering a relaxed yet polished look.
outfit_data.bottom: Wide-leg khaki flannel trousers with a sharp, angular cut. The fabric has a subtle plaid pattern in muted earth tones, adding visual interest without being overly bold.
outfit_data.shoes: Black leather Chelsea boots with sturdy rubber soles. The ankle height and pointed toe offer a touch of formality while remaining practical for navigating sandy terrain.
outfit_data.extras: A long, taupe-colored wool duster coat draped over the shoulders adds warmth and an air of effortless sophistication. Accessorize with simple gold hoop earrings and a brown leather belt cinched around the waist to accentuate the masculine silhouette.
